[[File:Vladimir Putin with Aslanbek Aslakhanov-1.jpg|thumb|250px|On right, with Vladimir Putin on left. 2000 ]] '''Aslambek Akhmedovich Aslakhanov''' (Асламбек Ахметович Аслаханов, born 11 March 1942 in [[Novye Atagi]]) is the State [[Duma]] deputy from [[Chechnya]], advisor and former aide to Russian president [[Vladimir Putin]].
He is a retired General of the [[MVD]].
