==Magicians== * [[Doug Henning]] (1947–2000) – credited with reviving the magic show in North America * [[Leon Mandrake]] (1911–1993) – Mandrake the Great; and his sons Lon and Ron, born in 1948 and 1949, respectively * [[Darcy Oake]] (born 1987) – illusionist, born in Winnipeg, finalist on ''Britain's Got Talent'' * [[James Randi]] (born 1928) – magician, writer, skeptical investigator of paranormal and pseudo-scientific claims, founder of the [[James Randi Educational Foundation]] * [[Dai Vernon]] (1894–1992) – magician, known as "the man who fooled Houdini"
