l, currently living in Quebec * [[Sue Rodriguez]] (1950–1994) – [[amyotrophic lateral sclerosis]] (ALS) sufferer and [[right to die]] advocate * [[Alexander Milton Ross]] (1832–1897) (known as The Birdman) – pre-[[American Civil War]] [[Abolitionism in the United States|abolitionist]] and participant in the [[Underground Railroad]] * [[Craig Russell (Canadian actor)|Craig Russell]] (1948–1990) – [[female impersonator]] and [[actor]] * [[Laura Secord]] (1775–1868) – heroine of the [[War of 1812]], warned the British of a surprise American attack at [[Battle of Beaver Dams]] * [[Joshua Slocum]] (1844–1909) – first man to sail around the world solo * [[Margaret Trudeau]] (1948) – former wife of [[Pierre Elliott Trudeau]]
