{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2018}} {{BLP sources|date=October 2016}} {{Infobox person | name = Mike Lewis | image = Mike Lewis.JPG | caption = | birth_name = Michael George William Lewis | birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1981|10|22}} | birth_place = [[Tokyo]], [[Japan]] | nationality = Canadian-Malaysian | home_town = [[Jakarta]], [[Indonesia]] | other_names = | occupation = [[Actor]], [[Model (person)|model]] | years_active = 2001&ndash; present | spouse = | children = Kenzou Lion Bleszynski Lewis | known_for = The Sexiest Cosmo Man for 2004 | alma_mater = }}
'''Michael George William''' "'''Mike'''" '''Lewis'''<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2012/12/02/feet-kitchen-eyes-hollywood.html|title=Feet in the kitchen, eyes on Hollywood|last=Prathivi|first=Niken|date=2 December 2012|work=The Jakarta Post|access-date=10 October 2016|via=}}</ref> (born 22 October 1981) is an Indonesian citizen actor and model. His father is a Canadian diplomat while his mother is Chinese Malaysian. When he was still in high school his father was stationed at Canada embassy in Jakarta. As of 2018, he currently resides in Jakarta.<ref>http://daman.co.id/mike-lewis-exclusive-interview-and-photoshoot</ref><ref>http://m.tribunnews.com/seleb/2016/05/01/mike-lewis-hamili-model-amerika</ref>
== Career == Besides working for some Indonesian agencies, he also works for international agency, Specs Agency in Canada and in addition as the staff of Canada Embassy in Indonesia. In 2003 he played his first film "5 Sehat, 4 Sempurna". He became The Sexiest Cosmo Man according to Cosmopolitan Magazine for 2 years in a row, 2004 and 2005. During 2005 to 2006 he went to and fro Montreal-Jakarta for modeling jobs.
